name: The Golden Temple of Amritsar. Original unframed photograph.
description:
This limited edition Giclee Print is produced on Fotospeed EG FineArt Platinum Baryta 300gsm (containing Barium Sulphate to provide a smooth unglazed glossy finish and stunning colours). 100% Acid Free. 

Image size is 15" x 10" with caption and print number printed below, over all size is A3 leaving plenty of white border for multiple framing options. Supplied unmounted and rolled for safe postage.

This image is featured on the front cover of 2011 edition of Lonely Planet India.
